@startuml
title ATM - Amount Selection and Transaction Verification

[*] --> Idle

state Idle
state WaitingForAmountSelection
state ValidatingTransaction
state RejectedTransaction

Idle --> WaitingForAmountSelection : User Initiates Withdrawal

WaitingForAmountSelection --> ValidatingTransaction : Amount Selected / Validate Transaction
WaitingForAmountSelection --> ValidatingTransaction : Custom Amount Entered / Validate Transaction

ValidatingTransaction --> RejectedTransaction : Transaction Rejected / Display Rejection
RejectedTransaction --> WaitingForAmountSelection : Re-enter Amount Requested

@enduml
